Subject: [PATCH 4/5] Add r_streams.h include for R-compatible output
 declarations

Include config/r_streams.h in spxdefines.h so that r_cerr()/r_cout()
declarations are available without the old r_remap.h force-include.
---
 src/soplex/spxdefines.h | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/src/soplex/spxdefines.h b/src/soplex/spxdefines.h
index 6f0a2866..1ea338fe 100644
--- a/src/soplex/spxdefines.h
+++ b/src/soplex/spxdefines.h
@@ -48,6 +48,7 @@
 #include <stdarg.h>
 #include <stdio.h>
 #include <ostream>
+#include "r_streams.h"
 
 #include <cstdlib>
 #include <memory>
